00:56.223 --> 00:59.226
[video game music]

01:02.521 --> 01:04.398
Hey, Benji, can you
pause that for a second?

01:04.398 --> 01:06.275
- Yeah, sure. What's up?
[beep]

01:07.985 --> 01:09.903
- So, I was just updating my iPad,

01:09.903 --> 01:11.905
and, uh, it synced to the family cloud,

01:11.905 --> 01:15.242
and, obviously, there were pictures
from your laptop on there.

01:15.242 --> 01:16.827
- What pictures?

01:18.328 --> 01:21.248
- Pictures of shirtless men,
pictures of pantless men, pictures of--

01:21.248 --> 01:22.666
Name an article of clothing,

01:22.666 --> 01:24.877
there was a picture of a man
not wearing that.

01:26.837 --> 01:28.714
- Uh... [nervous laugh]

01:28.714 --> 01:30.841
Oh... Oh god. Um...

01:30.841 --> 01:33.510
I-I think I know what happened.

01:33.510 --> 01:35.179
I lent my laptop to Lucy,

01:35.179 --> 01:37.806
and she is just completely boy-crazy.

01:39.016 --> 01:40.726
- [laughs] Oh, thank God.

01:42.269 --> 01:43.562
Oh, for a second there, I thought--

01:43.562 --> 01:45.814
I mean, not that there's
anything wrong with being gay.

01:45.814 --> 01:47.482
I just never thought
my son would be, you know?

01:47.482 --> 01:49.151
- Because I'm not.

01:49.151 --> 01:52.446
- Hello, darlings. What are
my two favorite guys up for?

01:52.446 --> 01:54.615
- [sighs] Morgan, oh my god.

01:54.615 --> 01:56.325
You're gonna die.
The funniest thing just happened.

01:56.325 --> 01:57.910
- Oh good. I need a good story.

01:57.910 --> 02:00.913
