02:07.753 --> 02:09.254
[bottle sloshing]

02:19.765 --> 02:22.351
♪ Somebody to tell me it'll be alright ♪

02:22.351 --> 02:25.354
♪ Somebody to tell me it'll be just fine ♪

02:25.354 --> 02:28.398
♪ Yeah, someone who's been there before
to say right now ♪

02:28.398 --> 02:30.692
♪ 'Cause I just need to hear it ♪

02:35.989 --> 02:38.408
[cafe chatter]
[quiet music playing]

02:38.408 --> 02:41.411
VICTOR: Uh, so h-how are things
with your uncle?

02:41.411 --> 02:44.331
- Still homophobic enough that I have
to wear corduroy around him,

02:44.331 --> 02:46.500
and not chic corduroy.

02:46.500 --> 02:47.793
Rugged corduroy.

02:48.252 --> 02:51.171
- Well, uh, how's your mom? H-how are...

02:51.171 --> 02:52.464
How are things at work?

02:52.464 --> 02:55.509
- Stop stalling and ask me
what you want to ask me already.

02:56.844 --> 02:59.680
- How's tutoring Benji going?
- There it is!

03:00.264 --> 03:02.808
I'm sitting right here.
Am I supposed to not eavesdrop?

03:04.226 --> 03:05.394
- Let's go.

03:05.394 --> 03:07.229
It's just weird that
now you guys are friends,

03:07.229 --> 03:08.814
and he still won't talk to me.

03:09.481 --> 03:11.567
I understand that everyone
thinks that this is what's best

03:11.567 --> 03:13.193
for his recovery, but how bad is it

03:13.193 --> 03:15.904
to talk to the person that cares
about you more than anything?

03:16.280 --> 03:18.282
- Victor, I say this with love.

03:19.199 --> 03:20.701
Stop obsessing over Benji

03:20.701 --> 03:23.829
or I'm going to stuff my head in that
coffee grinder and crank it to 10.

03:24.997 --> 03:27.291
ANDREW: If you want my advice...
BOTH: No.

03:27.291 --> 03:30.878
- the best way to get over someone
is to get under somebody else.

03:30.878 --> 03:33.630
- I actually agree
with handsome and crude here.

03:35.716 --> 03:38.302
- Well, I did download that dating app

03:38.302 --> 03:40.345
you told me about.
- No way. Really?

03:41.430 --> 03:42.055
[beep]

03:42.973 --> 03:45.267
Oh my God. Look at you.

03:45.267 --> 03:46.810
You're four and a half feet away from me.

03:47.895 --> 03:49.521
Victor, what is this profile?

03:49.521 --> 03:51.481
No picture, no name.

03:51.481 --> 03:52.858
Serial killer vibes.

03:52.858 --> 03:55.652
-It's just, you know, I'm not ready
to put my face out there yet.

03:55.652 --> 03:58.655
- Okay, but you really have to give people
something to work with, so...

04:00.824 --> 04:03.160
Your name is...
- Diego.

04:03.160 --> 04:05.162
You're strong, dangerous,

04:05.829 --> 04:07.039
wild in bed.

04:07.664 --> 04:08.874
- You're weirdly good at this.

04:08.874 --> 04:11.084
- Thank you.
- Okay. Diego.

04:11.084 --> 04:12.711
You're 22.
[typing]

04:12.711 --> 04:14.838
Hold on. Let me find a torso pic
that looks like you.

04:14.838 --> 04:16.298
- Do you want one of mine?

04:16.298 --> 04:18.467
