04:24.139 --> 04:25.807
- Can you let go of my hand?

04:25.807 --> 04:27.684
- Pilar, your parents know about us, okay?

04:27.684 --> 04:30.854
We don't need to hide our love.
On top of that, never letting go.

04:30.854 --> 04:32.439
- I need to get out my keys.

04:33.857 --> 04:35.484
- Right. Yeah.
- Yeah.

04:36.985 --> 04:38.237
[keys jingling]

04:39.404 --> 04:40.864
¡Mi familia!

04:40.864 --> 04:42.199
- Pilar, inside.

04:46.161 --> 04:47.329
- Hey, is everything okay?

04:47.329 --> 04:48.539
- You go home.
- Whoa, whoa, whoa--

04:48.539 --> 04:50.457
- You are not welcome here anymore.

04:53.836 --> 04:55.796
