05:16.441 --> 05:17.442
Now, give me your phone.

05:17.442 --> 05:19.736
- Mom, can you tell Dad to chill?

05:19.736 --> 05:22.406
- You are under the mistaken impression
that I'm on your side.

05:22.406 --> 05:25.534
You stood there and you told us
no more secrets.

05:25.534 --> 05:27.327
And then, we find these in your room!

05:27.327 --> 05:28.579
Give him your phone, Pilar!

05:28.579 --> 05:30.122
- You guys are being so crazy!

05:30.122 --> 05:33.542
- Laptop, iPad, and your watch.

05:33.542 --> 05:36.086
- Why her watch?
- Because watches have texting.

05:36.086 --> 05:37.588
- It's a Timex.

05:39.506 --> 05:43.135
- Alright, fine. Just keep the watch,
and go to your room.

05:43.135 --> 05:44.136
[huffs]

05:46.138 --> 05:49.141
