07:32.494 --> 07:33.662
- Cool.

07:34.538 --> 07:36.039
- Victor?

07:38.625 --> 07:39.835
- Benji?

07:40.752 --> 07:42.296
Hey, what are you doing here?

07:42.296 --> 07:45.299
- I'm just, uh, meeting someone.

07:46.842 --> 07:47.885
You?

07:48.385 --> 07:49.761
- Yeah. Uh, same.

07:50.512 --> 07:52.181
- Oh.
- Yeah.

08:00.022 --> 08:01.398
Lucas?

08:03.442 --> 08:04.693
- Diego.

08:04.693 --> 08:08.071
♪

08:11.658 --> 08:14.328
- I can't believe I meet up
with one guy

08:14.328 --> 08:17.206
from this stupid app, and-and it's you.

08:17.206 --> 08:18.832
And I can't believe you said you're 5'11"!

08:18.832 --> 08:22.085
- I can't believe you used that torso pic.
Whose abs are those?

08:22.085 --> 08:24.171
- You're a freshman at Emory.
Figure it out.

08:24.171 --> 08:25.422
[both laugh]

08:26.048 --> 08:27.090
Um...

08:27.090 --> 08:29.176
Are you supposed to be going on dates?

08:30.177 --> 08:33.263
I mean, in-in terms of your,
uh, your recovery?

08:34.598 --> 08:37.100
- Uh, no, not really.

08:38.644 --> 08:41.772
I just really needed
a distraction tonight.

08:42.981 --> 08:43.982
- Oh.

08:45.484 --> 08:46.985
Do you want to talk about it?

08:47.528 --> 08:50.781
- I was kind of hoping to forget
about my problems tonight.

08:51.365 --> 08:53.659
- Got it. Yeah. Um...

08:54.660 --> 08:57.788
Well, as much as I'd like to help you,
you know, get your mind off things,

08:59.039 --> 09:01.083
we're not really supposed
to be hanging out.

09:01.834 --> 09:02.876
So...

09:04.044 --> 09:05.712
- Well, I mean, Victor and Benji

09:05.712 --> 09:07.923
aren't supposed to be hanging out.

09:09.758 --> 09:11.552
I don't see why...

09:11.552 --> 09:13.053
Lucas and Diego can't.

09:13.929 --> 09:15.347
Just for tonight.

09:16.348 --> 09:18.684
- Yeah. Yeah. Just-just for tonight.

09:21.854 --> 09:23.105
- Come on, Diego.

09:24.773 --> 09:26.400
- That's me. [laughs]

09:27.943 --> 09:29.945
[walkie-talkie beep, static]
- Hello?

09:30.487 --> 09:32.489
Felix? Are you there?
[static]

09:33.532 --> 09:35.576
FELIX [over walkie-talkie]:
Yeah, I'm here. I was worried.

09:35.576 --> 09:37.286
Are you okay? Over.

09:37.286 --> 09:40.122
- I'm fine. Over.
Okay, yeah, I'm not doing that.

09:40.122 --> 09:41.790
Let's just talk like normal people.

09:41.790 --> 09:43.584
- Okay. Um, Pilar, what's going on?

09:44.001 --> 09:45.836
[sighs]
[click]

09:46.461 --> 09:49.089
- My parents found
birth control in my room.

09:49.548 --> 09:51.717
- What? Okay, uh...

09:51.717 --> 09:53.719
