if we're not even...

09:55.429 --> 09:57.097
Do I not know how sex works?

09:57.097 --> 09:58.182
[click]

09:58.182 --> 10:00.559
- I just wanted to be prepared.

10:00.559 --> 10:03.228
I mean, we're in love, and...

10:03.228 --> 10:05.480
