were headed that way, so.

10:06.565 --> 10:08.775
- Yeah, definitely. I mean,
you know, I-I-I...

10:09.401 --> 10:12.196
I was kind of, yeah, I was--
I was definitely having high hopes...

10:12.196 --> 10:15.282
for that. Uh-- I mean,
when you're ready. Of course.

10:15.282 --> 10:18.493
