heading that way part,

10:20.787 --> 10:24.666
but the Felix-isn't-having-sex-
with-their-daughter part.

10:25.250 --> 10:28.212
[click]
- I tried to, but they think I'm lying.

10:29.505 --> 10:32.549
[click]
- Yeah. Yeah, I get that.

10:32.549 --> 10:34.718
[click]
