more than we already have.

11:24.768 --> 11:26.144
[static]
Pilar?

11:29.273 --> 11:31.608
Pilar, are you there? Over?
[static]

11:37.823 --> 11:40.117
- Over.
[beep]

11:40.117 --> 11:42.744
