12:00.095 --> 12:01.930
DRAG QUEEN:
Everyone's favorite vitamin, B12!

12:01.930 --> 12:02.973
- Yeah.

12:03.348 --> 12:05.392
- I-I'm sorry. I-I just...

12:05.392 --> 12:07.394
