12:09.730 --> 12:11.857
DRAG QUEEN: G46.
I see you're up to the same old tricks...

12:11.857 --> 12:15.319
- Am I being awkward?
I feel like I'm being really awkward.

12:15.319 --> 12:18.197
- Let's just keep things light.

12:18.197 --> 12:20.574
Okay? Lucas. Diego.

12:21.200 --> 12:22.492
DRAG QUEEN:
I29.

12:22.492 --> 12:25.370
I also like 69,
but that's a different game.

12:25.370 --> 12:27.539
[laughter]

12:29.124 --> 12:30.834
- Okay, Lucas.

12:31.627 --> 12:33.420
What did you major in?
- Music.

12:33.420 --> 12:36.256
- Oh. My ex-boyfriend was a musician.

12:36.256 --> 12:38.467
- Mm. Sounds dreamy.
- Yes.

12:38.467 --> 12:40.177
Very dreamy.

12:40.177 --> 12:42.179
He was my first boyfriend and...

12:42.971 --> 12:44.014
my first love.

12:45.265 --> 12:46.767
My first...

12:47.684 --> 12:48.685
You know.

12:49.520 --> 12:51.980
DRAG QUEEN:
B8! Don't you ask me my weight!

12:51.980 --> 12:55.442
