Honey, I'm N2 anyone who's N2 me!

13:06.036 --> 13:08.080
Beggars can't be choosers, am I right?

13:08.080 --> 13:10.541
[laughter]
- Bingo!

13:10.541 --> 13:13.377
DRAG QUEEN: Oh! Damn!
